info.description:
Castellan is a key manager interface with configurable back ends. The
UI supports managing private keys, public keys, symmetric keys, certificates,
passphrases, and opaque data. The UI also supports generating public, private,
and symmetric keys.
info.name: castellan-ui
info.summary: The Castellan UI plugin for Horizon allows users to view and manage key manager objects such as keys and certificates needed for OpenStack’s encryption features.
